title: Nazara Tech Q4 Results: Profit rises 17% to Rs 4.9 cr - Economic Times
content: Nazara Tech Q4 Results: Profit rises 17% to Rs 4.9 cr  Economic Times
description: Revenue from operations increased by about 42 per cent to Rs 175.1 crore during the reported quarter from Rs 123.4 crore in the year-ago period.
